WEBVTT

1
00:00:60.000 --> 00:00:69.000
<v Inglis, Jake>So firstly, could you just tell us a little about yourself?</v>

2
00:00:70.000 --> 00:00:78.500
<v Reyes, Maria>Sure. I grew up in Cebu and moved to London about ten years ago for work.</v>

3
00:00:79.000 --> 00:00:88.000
<v Reyes, Maria>Food was the thing I missed most, especially dried fish in the morning.</v>

4
00:00:89.000 --> 00:00:99.000
<v Inglis, Jake>That's lovely. And how do you keep those traditions going here?</v>

5
00:01:40.000 --> 00:01:52.000
<v Reyes, Maria>We cook together every Sunday. My kids now ask for adobo before anything else.</v>
